as marketing gets, is more digital nowadays and is being executed through all sorts of

00:22:13.839 --> 00:22:19.739
different social media platforms or other online platforms, what you might be able to

00:22:19.739 --> 00:22:24.140
extract out of those platforms may not be in the best form for a model.

00:22:24.140 --> 00:22:27.500
It might not be in the most ideal form that you'd want, you know.

00:22:27.500 --> 00:22:34.459
Let's say you have, you know, new customer signups by day, just some generic term, right?

00:22:34.459 --> 00:22:42.099
