00:22:42.099 --> 00:22:47.939
So there's a lot of, you know, there's assumptions you can make about spreading some of that

00:22:47.979 --> 00:22:51.500
data around to try and get it to fit the structure you need for building a model.

00:22:51.500 --> 00:22:57.739
