00:22:57.739 --> 00:23:00.939
You know, if you like data munging, it's a great space to be in because you get data

00:23:00.939 --> 00:23:03.619
from all these disparate systems and it's all in different formats.

00:23:03.619 --> 00:23:08.459
And, you know, your job is to, you know, blend it in a way that makes logical sense for

00:23:08.459 --> 00:23:13.020
explaining the problem that you're working on.

00:23:13.099 --> 00:23:19.180
The pros, I'll say, and this is the most obvious one, is that, you know, you can have a conversation

00:23:19.180 --> 00:23:23.939
