00:23:30.619 --> 00:23:33.579
outcome and a different channels has contributed this.

00:23:33.579 --> 00:23:36.859
And had you done this instead, this might've been the outcome.

00:23:36.859 --> 00:23:41.579
And, you know, you can test that going forward and, you know, over the next quarter or six

00:23:41.619 --> 00:23:47.260
months or whatever. And a lot of times that's eye-opening for, for a CMO.

00:23:47.260 --> 00:23:52.500
There's a lot of pressure, I think, on CMOs, chief marketing officers these days, to show

00:23:52.500 --> 00:23:53.619
they spend a lot of money, right?

00:23:53.619 --> 00:23:57.260
