00:24:15.420 --> 00:24:20.739
So if you've got a tool that can consider all the things you're doing where the spend

00:24:20.739 --> 00:24:25.300
all adds up to your total budget and the outcomes all add up to what was observed by the whole

00:24:25.300 --> 00:24:31.300
organization and you can say, you know, based on our model, we think that, you know, Facebook

00:24:31.300 --> 00:24:34.699
did this or Google did this or Direct Mail did this.

00:24:34.699 --> 00:24:40.300
And so now you can, now that CMO can have a much, you know, much better conversation

00:24:40.300 --> 00:24:45.979
